234
00:20:25,558 --> 00:20:26,679
Do you see that berth number?

235
00:20:27,099 --> 00:20:29,681
Take a look.
- Number seven

236
00:20:29,851 --> 00:20:32,813
Coach FC 1, berth number 7

237
00:20:33,643 --> 00:20:34,974
Always reserved for..

238
00:20:35,064 --> 00:20:38,686
the Fursatganj staff
going to Lucknow. I've been..

239
00:20:38,776 --> 00:20:40,818
..using this berth for 3 years

240
00:20:41,988 --> 00:20:47,612
The entire railway
division knows that.

241
00:20:47,692 --> 00:20:49,323
How could anyone
have given it to you?

242
00:20:50,284 --> 00:20:51,985
Could you tug that
chain for me please?

243
00:21:34,311 --> 00:21:37,433
You think you're the first
person to come up with this idea?

244
00:21:37,893 --> 00:21:41,065
We spend eight hours a day in offices
like this, chewing tobacco, eh?

245
00:21:41,355 --> 00:21:43,766
200 out of every 100 finance companies
dream of a scheme like this..

246
00:21:43,816 --> 00:21:46,268
but trip over their own two feet..

247
00:21:46,358 --> 00:21:53,482
..trying to find 500 investors
to chip in a thousand rupees each

248
00:21:53,823 --> 00:21:55,984
The answer to my next
question is on your face but..

249
00:21:56,114 --> 00:22:00,907
I'll ask you anyway.. Mister,
where are your 500 investors?

250
00:22:02,158 --> 00:22:03,909
What if I tell you I have them?

251
00:22:04,289 --> 00:22:05,740
Where?

252
00:22:06,450 --> 00:22:07,451
Here

253
00:22:11,203 --> 00:22:13,124
I've slogged it out
for a whole year, sir

254
00:22:13,625 --> 00:22:15,336
I've gotten together 500 investors..

255
00:22:15,456 --> 00:22:17,627
..from my town and
the neighbouring ones..

256
00:22:17,837 --> 00:22:21,169
..willing to put up a thousand rupees
each in any good finance company

257
00:22:22,130 --> 00:22:23,251
Where are you from?

258
00:22:23,551 --> 00:22:25,042
Fursatganj

259
00:22:26,593 --> 00:22:31,466
Fursatganj! Where l was once

260
00:22:31,556 --> 00:22:34,007
Not one finance company..

261
00:22:34,137 --> 00:22:39,221
..will waste five minutes
over a list like this one.

262
00:22:39,511 --> 00:22:41,972
Talk of investments

263
00:22:42,853 --> 00:22:47,145
Small town-guys have a habit of
dreaming big. No ban on dreaming..

264
00:22:47,225 --> 00:22:48,896
..Indulge yourself

265
00:22:49,147 --> 00:22:51,558
But next time, come up
with a scheme that..

266
00:22:51,648 --> 00:22:58,522
..a thousand others haven't thought
up before you. Get it? Now excuse me

267
00:23:12,241 --> 00:23:14,702
Where are you going, lady?
- To enter the contest

268
00:23:14,912 --> 00:23:17,744
You can't go in.
- If l can't go inside..

269
00:23:17,834 --> 00:23:19,165
..how do I take part
in the competition?

270
00:23:19,285 --> 00:23:20,876
Let me in. l've come really far

271
00:23:21,166 --> 00:23:24,748
I said, you can't go in.
- I say, I have to enter

272
00:23:30,502 --> 00:23:33,464
Can l help you?
- Yes, myself Vimmi Saluja..

273
00:23:33,544 --> 00:23:35,675
I've come to enter the contest.
- You're too late

274
00:23:35,755 --> 00:23:39,007
What?
- The entries closed two days ago

275
00:23:39,297 --> 00:23:41,469
You mean the contest's begun?
- No, not yet

276
00:23:41,549 --> 00:23:44,431
Oh, that's a relief.
- I said, entries have closed

277
00:23:44,511 --> 00:23:48,263
But the contest hasn't begun!
- I said "the-entries-have-closed"

278
00:23:48,513 --> 00:23:50,554
So open up for two minutes,
I'll quickly squeeze in!

279
00:23:50,724 --> 00:23:53,646
You're from some village?
Miss Quickly-squeeze-in!

280
00:23:53,726 --> 00:23:57,689
This is no village fair to
squeeze-in-slip-out when-you-wish

281
00:23:57,859 --> 00:24:01,101
This is the Miss lndia contest,
but what would you know?

282
00:24:01,441 --> 00:24:03,442
Oh c'mon Pammi, forget it

283
00:24:03,562 --> 00:24:07,155
One minute.. would I know what?
- The desire and the ability..

284
00:24:07,235 --> 00:24:10,487
..to become Miss lndia are two
very different things. So go home..

285
00:24:10,567 --> 00:24:15,910
..and start a beauty parlour.
- Why not beauty-parlour yourself?

286
00:24:15,990 --> 00:24:17,911
Excuse me?
- Ever watched your figure?

287
00:24:18,161 --> 00:24:19,862
At least ten kilos overweight..

288
00:24:19,952 --> 00:24:22,414
Ever watched your figure? At
least ten kilos overweight..

289
00:24:22,494 --> 00:24:26,246
..with miles-thick lipstick.
You know all about make-up.

290
00:24:26,326 --> 00:24:28,117
Beauty parlour's for you

291
00:24:28,208 --> 00:24:29,168
What a bitch

292
00:24:29,288 --> 00:24:30,709
You bitch

293
00:24:36,883 --> 00:24:46,889
-=Deathracer=-

294
00:25:00,017 --> 00:25:00,978
Listen..

295
00:25:03,269 --> 00:25:06,731
Yes?
- Please come with me to the toilet

296
00:25:07,812 --> 00:25:12,855
It's right at the end of the
platform and it's really dark

297
00:25:18,108 --> 00:25:19,199
Come

298
00:25:25,613 --> 00:25:28,324
Weren't you on the
Jhansi Mail this morning?

299
00:25:30,326 --> 00:25:32,247
Returning? Here on business?

300
00:25:32,997 --> 00:25:37,870
Yes I came for the
Miss India contest

301
00:25:40,752 --> 00:25:43,464
So how was it?

302
00:25:45,715 --> 00:25:48,337
Good.. very good

303
00:25:49,297 --> 00:25:52,049
I got through the first round

304
00:25:52,469 --> 00:25:55,921
Good.. good.. Miss India!

305
00:25:58,093 --> 00:26:02,425
And you? Here on business too?
- Oh no.. no..

306
00:26:02,936 --> 00:26:07,058
Work is something I
don't really believe in

307
00:26:07,769 --> 00:26:09,390
I came here for a meeting

308
00:26:10,440 --> 00:26:15,313
There's a finance company here,
they want to buy my scheme

309
00:26:16,984 --> 00:26:21,067
I had to come personally you see,
it's a matter of millions

310
00:26:22,778 --> 00:26:29,362
So, you're becoming a model soon?
- I guess so

311
00:26:30,533 --> 00:26:35,496
You'll become famous.
- Yes.. I guess so

312
00:26:36,656 --> 00:26:39,448
People will buzz around
you like bees around honey

313
00:26:39,708 --> 00:26:42,950
Yes.. I guess they will

314
00:26:48,374 --> 00:26:51,626
Why are you crying?

315
00:26:52,046 --> 00:26:53,707
I didn't mean to insult you

316
00:26:53,917 --> 00:26:55,588
No, don't take me otherwise

317
00:26:58,260 --> 00:27:04,093
I belong to a decent family,
I wouldn't dream of it

318
00:27:04,804 --> 00:27:07,175
Calm down, everyone's watching

319
00:27:08,266 --> 00:27:11,558
Poor thing.. she's in grieving

320
00:27:11,848 --> 00:27:13,559
I was only sympathising..

321
00:27:16,021 --> 00:27:17,852
Everything's fine

322
00:27:17,982 --> 00:27:19,853
Mummy.

323
00:27:25,106 --> 00:27:27,978
You'll be the first girl to cry after
making it to the Miss India contest

324
00:27:34,862 --> 00:27:38,735
I didn't make it anywhere

325
00:27:41,997 --> 00:27:43,868
Aren't you ashamed of lying?

326
00:27:51,162 --> 00:27:53,744
Actually, I lied too..

327
00:27:54,704 --> 00:27:57,836
..the manager of the finance
company didn't quite buy my scheme..

328
00:27:57,956 --> 00:28:00,338
I think he doesn't have the drive

329
00:28:02,169 --> 00:28:03,250
Bloody idiot

330
00:28:03,340 --> 00:28:07,923
Foulmouthing.. me?

331
00:28:08,263 --> 00:28:10,554
Escort her to the loo
and then get abused for it?

332
00:28:11,015 --> 00:28:14,637
I escorted you! Who
do you think you are?

333
00:28:22,311 --> 00:28:27,144
You mean if you go back now?
- Wedding bells..

334
00:28:28,525 --> 00:28:31,437
That's too bad.
- Very

335
00:28:32,278 --> 00:28:33,358
Then?

336
00:28:37,651 --> 00:28:39,442
I'll run away.

337
00:28:42,574 --> 00:28:45,196
You already have

338
00:28:47,197 --> 00:28:52,870
So, what'll you do now?
- What'll you do?

339
00:28:55,952 --> 00:28:59,664
Whatever I do, I'm not giving up.
And l'm not going back home

340
00:28:59,744 --> 00:29:01,035
Then, where will you go?

341
00:29:05,048 --> 00:29:06,339
Kanpur

342
00:29:06,959 --> 00:29:11,292
Why Kanpur? - The
company has a head office there

343
00:29:11,422 --> 00:29:15,544
I'll show my scheme to senior
officers, I'm sure they'll get it

344
00:29:17,966 --> 00:29:20,717
Why don't you come along to Kanpur?
- Who me?

345
00:29:21,098 --> 00:29:24,510
Miss India contests
are held all over.

346
00:29:24,600 --> 00:29:26,301
Maybe they'll allow
you to enter there

347
00:29:27,722 --> 00:29:30,724
You got to find a
way into the contest..

348
00:29:30,814 --> 00:29:32,395
..else what use was running away?

349
00:29:34,896 --> 00:29:36,267
Kanpur!

350
00:29:57,160 --> 00:30:00,952
So long, l guess the next
time I see you it'll be on TV

351
00:30:01,412 --> 00:30:07,286
I guess so. Thank you. And
good luck for your big meeting

352
00:30:08,537 --> 00:30:10,328
Thanks but that was superfluous.

353
00:30:10,628 --> 00:30:13,250
I only need to make a
presentation and voila!

354
00:30:13,340 --> 00:30:16,422
I'll have 100 finance
companies running rings around me

355
00:30:18,383 --> 00:30:19,463
See you

356
00:30:23,846 --> 00:30:30,891
Unbelievable. Got to admit..
very few people have brains as sharp

357
00:30:31,391 --> 00:30:38,095
I say, just once in a whole year,
let me meet just one such person

358
00:30:38,305 --> 00:30:44,099
But two in a single day,
unbelievable!

359
00:30:45,309 --> 00:30:49,482
Would you believe..

360
00:30:50,022 --> 00:30:54,525
just half an hour ago, another man
came to me with an identical scheme

361
00:30:56,196 --> 00:31:00,489
Who?
- Manager of our Lucknow branch..

362
00:31:00,569 --> 00:31:06,112
Mr Qureishi! Imagine.. a rare
gem lay buried in my own backyard

363
00:31:07,073 --> 00:31:10,075
He got a 10,000 bonus on the spot!

364
00:31:11,035 --> 00:31:16,208
..He even had a
list of 500 investors.

365
00:31:16,419 --> 00:31:18,710
Unbelievable! What a man!
- Where's he staying?

366
00:31:19,080 --> 00:31:24,373
Landmark Hotel.
- In Landmark! And why not?

367
00:31:24,634 --> 00:31:27,005
The 10,000 bonus!

368
00:31:27,175 --> 00:31:34,049
Give me as much l'll go
to live in a five star too

369
00:31:34,219 --> 00:31:36,301
Next?
- Vimmi Saluja

370
00:31:36,721 --> 00:31:39,843
Address?
- 2/5 Ballygunj, Pankinagar

371
00:31:44,936 --> 00:31:46,637
One minute..

372
00:31:48,688 --> 00:31:53,351
Doesn't Pankinagar fall
within the Lucknow district?

373
00:31:53,771 --> 00:31:56,603
It does?
- Yes, Lucknow district

374
00:31:57,104 --> 00:31:59,645
You didn't fill up
the form in Lucknow?

375
00:32:00,065 --> 00:32:03,237
What difference, here or there?

376
00:32:03,317 --> 00:32:05,859
I was passing through Kanpur so
I thought I'll get it over with

377
00:32:06,279 --> 00:32:07,530
Very good

378
00:32:08,240 --> 00:32:10,362
Please step outside

379
00:32:11,072 --> 00:32:17,156
Sir'ji, just a matter of an address..
- Go away! Rules are rules

380
00:32:17,456 --> 00:32:19,457
Please..
- Get lost

381
00:32:20,038 --> 00:32:21,959
Oversmartness

382
00:32:30,424 --> 00:32:34,967
Look, l can't bend the rules

383
00:32:35,677 --> 00:32:39,840
But if you wish..

384
00:32:40,630 --> 00:32:42,421
I can forget rules for a while

385
00:32:43,222 --> 00:32:47,805
Yes sir!
- But nothing comes for free

386
00:32:47,885 --> 00:32:51,057
Sir, I'll do whatever you wish!

387
00:32:51,137 --> 00:32:55,349
Very good! Once you're Miss India..

388
00:32:55,439 --> 00:33:01,273
..you'll have all the wealth, all
the fame your heart ever desired

389
00:33:02,854 --> 00:33:07,357
But I? I'm still stuck to
the same.. chair and table

390
00:33:07,857 --> 00:33:10,319
Oh sure..

391
00:33:10,489 --> 00:33:12,820
I have nothing right now..

392
00:33:13,991 --> 00:33:16,783
but I promise, when l'm Miss India..

393
00:33:16,863 --> 00:33:20,535
I'll pay you..
everything you'll ever want

394
00:33:21,615 --> 00:33:28,870
You're mistaken. You have everything
I'll ever want.. right now

395
00:33:29,540 --> 00:33:35,664
I won't force you.
Registration closes in five minutes.

396
00:33:36,254 --> 00:33:37,916
Think it over

397
00:33:38,296 --> 00:33:41,168
You'll find me at the same table

398
00:34:22,903 --> 00:34:25,074
What's your name?
- Jajjan

399
00:34:25,905 --> 00:34:28,577
You make tea?
- No, I serve tea

400
00:34:34,951 --> 00:34:38,743
This world we live in boy,
has two kinds of people

401
00:34:38,833 --> 00:34:43,336
One, those who serve tea.
And those to whom tea is served

402
00:34:43,706 --> 00:34:45,627
The faster you
become one of the latter..

403
00:34:45,707 --> 00:34:47,458
..the better the
life that you'll live

404
00:34:47,838 --> 00:34:49,550
Has somebody hurt you?

405
00:34:58,305 --> 00:34:59,966
Two teas and chips

406
00:35:00,846 --> 00:35:02,097
Two?

407
00:35:02,518 --> 00:35:06,600
Why? Problem?
- No. But who's the second cup for?

408
00:35:07,180 --> 00:35:09,722
If l drink two cups,
will it start a war?

409
00:35:10,562 --> 00:35:14,475
God, this world we live in!
Get a hold on this kid

410
00:35:17,477 --> 00:35:20,108
It's no use.
- What?

411
00:35:21,229 --> 00:35:23,150
No use being earnest,

412
00:35:23,230 --> 00:35:26,072
unwitting fools getting
shoved in stinking little towns

413
00:35:26,322 --> 00:35:27,403
Then?

414
00:35:28,824 --> 00:35:29,984
Bombay..

415
00:35:31,325 --> 00:35:34,827
..the only city in all of lndia where
a man is recognised for his worth..

416
00:35:36,158 --> 00:35:38,910
the only place where you can start..

417
00:35:38,990 --> 00:35:41,742
..from the pavement
and end up in palaces..

418
00:35:41,832 --> 00:35:45,204
where ambition isn't pushed around,
but cheered, egging you on

419
00:35:45,624 --> 00:35:47,665
How're you so sure?
- How..

420
00:35:48,416 --> 00:35:52,668
if Dhirubhai Ambani, Ratan Tata,
Birla had been in Lucknow-Kanpur..

421
00:35:52,748 --> 00:35:55,380
..they'd be swatting flies in Ambani
General Stores, Tata Flour Mills..

422
00:35:55,460 --> 00:35:57,922
..And Birla Tobacco Stall.

423
00:35:58,382 --> 00:36:00,883
Bombay.. gave them the
recognition they deserved

424
00:36:01,054 --> 00:36:02,594
Look where it got them..

425
00:36:04,756 --> 00:36:07,758
So you want to go Bombay?

426
00:36:09,889 --> 00:36:12,681
You can come along too.
What'll you do here?

427
00:36:13,891 --> 00:36:15,763
All the top models are in Bombay.

428
00:36:16,103 --> 00:36:19,145
Damn this
narrow-minded small-town mob

429
00:36:19,895 --> 00:36:23,397
It's the place for Miss lndia, no?
- Yes

430
00:36:25,569 --> 00:36:29,561
A ticket to Bombay,
how much would it cost?

431
00:36:31,402 --> 00:36:33,403
Not that I have that kind of cash

432
00:36:40,528 --> 00:36:43,370
I got the cash, don't worry.
- What?

433
00:36:43,450 --> 00:36:46,201
We've seen where
truth has landed us.

434
00:36:46,281 --> 00:36:48,743
Now let's say what they want to hear

435
00:36:49,033 --> 00:36:52,995
And what's that?
- Oi Jajjan, where's Landmark Hotel?

436
00:36:55,247 --> 00:36:57,378
One whiskey..
- Which one sir?

437
00:36:58,289 --> 00:37:01,080
Imported. How much for a
Black Label? - Four hundred, sir

438
00:37:01,170 --> 00:37:02,882
For a bottle?
- No. 30 ml

439
00:37:03,292 --> 00:37:04,422
Small peg

440
00:37:04,713 --> 00:37:09,966
I'll try an Indian whiskey for a
change. And don't forget the peanuts

441
00:37:13,548 --> 00:37:17,220
Some pretty suave people you
got walking into this Gazal Bar

442
00:37:23,434 --> 00:37:25,395
One Black Label
- Sir

443
00:37:28,767 --> 00:37:31,649
Sir! You here?

444
00:37:31,729 --> 00:37:35,812
Fursatganj! All of Lucknow seems
to be pouring into Kanpur today

445
00:37:35,902 --> 00:37:39,814
Slick! What are you doing here?
- You'll be seeing more of me here

446
00:37:40,064 --> 00:37:43,907
What do you mean?
- My scheme got rocking

447
00:37:44,067 --> 00:37:47,739
Which.. the same one?
- No.. it was unworkable

448
00:37:47,819 --> 00:37:51,862
You tipped me off in time. I
could've wasted another good year

449
00:37:52,162 --> 00:37:56,494
This is another scheme.
- Which is this?

450
00:37:56,745 --> 00:38:00,037
I explained this scheme..

451
00:38:00,127 --> 00:38:03,249
..they offered me a two
per cent stake in the channel

452
00:38:03,789 --> 00:38:06,501
What channel?
- A news channel

453
00:38:07,381 --> 00:38:09,082
News channel

454
00:38:10,253 --> 00:38:16,087
Nowadays this news channel business
is taking off like a rocket

455
00:38:16,507 --> 00:38:20,089
In 3 months, they're giving
investors a 300 per cent..

456
00:38:20,179 --> 00:38:21,380
..return on investment

457
00:38:21,470 --> 00:38:24,512
Cigarette?
- Really?

458
00:38:24,592 --> 00:38:28,764
How much.. is the investment?
- At least 100,000

459
00:38:29,014 --> 00:38:35,348
Won't they take a little less?
I mean, I could invest too?

460
00:38:35,478 --> 00:38:38,230
Why don't you have a chat?

461
00:38:42,733 --> 00:38:44,734
Give me an introduction

462
00:38:51,158 --> 00:38:55,401
This is Mr. Qureishi
- Q.Q. Qureishi

463
00:38:55,741 --> 00:38:59,033
Q.Q. Qureishi, a very dear friend.

464
00:38:59,243 --> 00:39:04,576
Whatever I am
today is because of him

465
00:39:05,747 --> 00:39:09,039
Hello.
- Hello

466
00:39:12,541 --> 00:39:18,875
Mr. Qureishi would like
to invest in the channel

467
00:39:19,295 --> 00:39:20,966
How many millions?

468
00:39:23,008 --> 00:39:26,920
He's not like other investors..
this is just a friendly gesture..

469
00:39:27,010 --> 00:39:29,131
about ten thousand?
- Ten

470
00:39:29,932 --> 00:39:31,423
Ten?

471
00:39:32,263 --> 00:39:33,804
Fifteen?
- Fifteen?

472
00:39:34,975 --> 00:39:38,427
But you're aware, it
should be at least..

473
00:39:40,098 --> 00:39:43,850
Ok, all right, now
how can l refuse you?

474
00:39:47,563 --> 00:39:48,984
One request..

475
00:39:49,234 --> 00:39:55,147
..this remains between us..
let this be our little secret

476
00:39:55,237 --> 00:39:58,780
No, no!
- Promise

477
00:40:00,491 --> 00:40:03,533
We must be in Delhi by morning

478
00:40:04,403 --> 00:40:08,115
So you take the cash from him..

479
00:40:08,456 --> 00:40:11,247
..and fetch us a
receipt from my room. - Okay.

